: "Good, spacious courts with low dividing nets. They give you three good balls for free, and the court surface is new.", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2soOeIRc4_lgA_3DOHnwUzRHJh2fnBZqvezSCyqeac0h7d1ajTMcbwDv9Yd7OTIwqV9Q8_7l4L4SNQzvF99qecqCCJtRfZ5CGbg2K0_p1bGFhFurAHB0wggFRDierI1mfDEYHz7uWoRCXC=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0UmNzeZFyRgfkFdwmtqiUupsq2PrD7b7ETwoZsoTvoXsuV7m25ZoGTY06-kIngUkRvpCJ8zbm3lLKQKsz-o6cRfdjFTTHg44iVAJoTt_vO3sije8_oNenwH3LvRqgzYG0U8sAJmho2tcKj=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3zSBhae6JFQWszhrn3nyIuHd8dAl80m7CwtKpKs7jOdVXiHCBAZ8OkFgSknyEU7W7Zu5sVxgCYwdrbAb7PSLaM7zyX67ROSkDQu-BPq3fuxlvVPFRJ_1OsBZ1-IG9ar_N00DXkMvaQPdKF=k-no"], "When": "2025-9-17"}, {"Name": "Lê Nguyên Khoa Võ", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtyQWIhRXN7MpwsrPt4HiXGW7ig7FxwSilYsTGAc8M82bB8-1Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Large, beautiful yard. Good service", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Linh I''m", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ3d996IsfEZmhp1v8cZ7R6NFrcpBZStEzNthc7XSrBYn_Yjg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Great", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "mArIn Life with Beach", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWL3UeYx-rJeURQHCX6vKLxLrFUObWZs32ZkPOY4jg92GXC7Bf_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "3面のコートがあるピックルボールコートです。\n\nコートは綺麗で、エンドラインの後ろにも余裕があり、プレイしやすい環境が整っています。\n\nシャワー完備、売店完備のため、利便性も高いです。\nダナンのちょうど中心に位置しており、街側からも海側からもアクセスが良いのが魅力です。\n\nありがとうございました。また行きます！🏓🎾", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Uvps9m7iPVOQg0zGZ-hp4t8jF_7gksM_UVn7Evw2E-QzB9l9UI0uzJUA_e5uYcYuJJVW0zbVFLcC1e0Q5yGXkmI9_moASOXl-WvFL5vwLjnUyW2v5Drz_J7QdRSZgOc9NyztNOsfMQbk=k-no"], "When": "2025-12-2"}, {"Name": "Eat and travel", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkLXv2WDzeA_d_DXObA_BwabbFxFnL8jnVLiOucvqdhyWGDGzY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100", "Rating": 4, "Description": "不過唔錯嘅場地，可惜我們沒有預約，這次沒法感受着你的質量", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2vjxthTgzixWt3jWzkN1-bn3DyUWJpSFnRooAmjYWZU9a4OA-CyTwZqnI0ZNo0_MjCQvQJqmk0hSlKb__Kzhm6H0zXW3Vah41QzmPbPWLIcG_J_hPtnSC4h-27mGDH_T01iUYyDYsCsAY-=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1vFCByv0bTyknVWgsZFwIOHsLSfP1Gbk32lGjcitfNxMTA8NzH0LkR9uQmAQlonK5-2qW9Vs8NwP0MMQnWWzeqE3bUkTLX1j7syibxG36IjJ_XLUq3O9Do77UTvJY6gP3c_UHYjDEdY54=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1N_ynXETzYtaRDrGQd36u0N-EloQO7hp4TtvXF_H_VOyxtRhB0tNfYFcNsrT2YgJvAZIFVb4CnsOpnSkUKi5IaoP8dOcbZIV8HTTW9AlkkzPAtkkuRw6D9of8X5wfGd-0cCybiHHKgTRFP=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0SOxr9AyW2ZcoTHSx4luYRsL1TmAlBpyr1UnPzTNLVWmiQDYRhbBgH-ubdnZb4cUyLP3OoVXRC_T6L9-T63KP51g_JwTfv_sDYPElbxtIYTJyFswZ6QE17hO96chHMq5Rxg2mJyR0Qrgk=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0hHIv9ZgaWrKVMsoKfGJWS0sYNxhsBlZpLdE0yT5fg-zVSWl0veHaCQZz7TQWHkAcWAFdKWA3DfSb9vkK9Pr1IMNzY27-JCGlw7fdEFI0H7dvtSn_Ob6wPq01_Lu-N9x7I9u6kPjCyTM7r=k-no"], "When": "2025-9-29"}, {"Name": "까꿍", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpWFgcGdEsuDRkZOyHA50vPKZbzYpX_9IYogYspX1GH9-mEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "여기최고에요. 매일 밤7시 ~10시 , 5만동 게스트모집해서 재미있게 치고왔어요. 샤워시설있고, 넘좋음", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Vadim Larin", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHkHugOIAn_qWA7GtZPr0wIGQYr5BPXyv3SWzv9YiGZkzkBBI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 1, "Description": "Khung kim loại giữa các sân rất thấp, khó nhận thấy và không được đánh dấu, tôi đã đập đầu rất mạnh vào đó và bị rách toạc", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Hà Linh Trần", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSxD8kauv-gsHRZfSYmaWus8OlvFLIwPIi_ukwGA1w31IJ1_yO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Sân mới, sạch đẹp, đèn được setup hợp lí, không bị chói và chắn tầm nhìn. Nhà vệ sinh sạch sẽ, có quạt mát