m.–10:30 p.m."], "Thursday": ["5:30 a.m.–10:30 p.m."], "Tuesday": ["5:30 a.m.–10:30 p.m."], "Wednesday": ["5:30 a.m.–10:30 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name": "Pavel Strabykin", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRkvJUZWhXrL9Xrmse6zZvft02PuCdjH_u_CP93wrSEhjiEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "It''s probably the best court in Da Nang. Perfect equipment, reasonable prices, free rackets & balls and excellent service! The owners do this not for money, but for people. They really care about you: there is some fruits provided free during the game, so you can recover. Last time manager even gave us a box of branded balls as a gift :) thank so much for such an awesome service!", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3BVUvJ-Y7-8yDbhZg6rYV0FbJreeKAB7F4JPu0zhUwbHrTXEHvYyLAdlMOIrHnqYqdhM7AZZPYBLGTvLcXmay701UqWnoamUkrcffovzH5bWa7ASM2JdyWnovQnZUTlxg4u2aAHnUGRuI0=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2DvaPu55xu7yonW1IGliZzz8wWXrIi5UTBf0cXkyKPF0SVzD9KgVeIBXyZu-yNG0rZOGvQ6k_ikA-v__UcXMDZdM-0NLxWlFZ51EPPneUT68F9kDEjrPjU7jZs-V9Us5CopnlMVtmXGPk=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3j2-lNeFa7e6snZ0LEJ68WNQB75s1HQ5-8ESMNzqQNiDy_TepRbzdb1z1-Bn5AMnxT3y0TQzVvtUlybvRlpTId1uk7TQWsaK55Hnhb8ErYwtb-D2nkOd0y3sPvSztMxJb47TSGD_lfekkz=k-no"], "When": "2025-11-25"}, {"Name": "Anna Belz", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4nCNG5MHttTQUVF622r2-p6U9Q7D3IkRjPc22F2kTur1DUTwc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "This court is more windy because it is separated by a net, not metal walls, we were there on a not very hot day, it was comfortable. The price on weekdays until 16:30 is 120,000, rackets s and balls are included in the price, the balls are right on the field, there is no limit on their number. The court is a standard size, comfortable. And since 15.04  the  courts are  separated by a net, it is really comfortable .There is also a fitting room, shower and  lockers. However, I did not use them and did not check with the administrator whether they are available to everyone.", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1rkopvOGr5NXEndGVzNHL_NtbAmgp7YrPUo7-ZOipvffMgesEVx5u12BVFn4j9Z4kW0DOMXey4cnF3SJ-XwoC8rvmT2mLgjqQuQBBFWKEPyYNpHzzeEwDvEVbxWM6mHcKAHeUY=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2elvKnbrZVYt-MFyN8-Ar7qF7AsJUJbi4l8IWRDhlBJFuBgF0ZG2mYVssJ7cILayOMhiRreoZ7impaxAIuTMPWAKZJekZis4PKVmVdIAqkez7McYRxIJxpSTpR6Q2mItSWMG8YIA=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0qOuw8iDsS8fkImO6Q7NM97AgidPj9bmkWibyQMd7HUvKOYTbMjz1yBkFoGRwoLm3Pf3jXYCQI_qFEw8bdS6t0WahVwE2YlKQy8vad2M7TEUF4-3BDJiqeo8pSu60MW3gO-gLhDQ=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Q2UoQG7cxRVbwsr6SNL62k7GeinyVacD55aZHdPDqkvKQkmPX5eoAVpxxIuNmeKd6MFq03Qri7nCJRdiidV9vHUwKHEzdSiXLEcJK5yMo43GgveB34m6zrjMzEBvFTkqeiSBDKQ=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2EmYh-FoK3fbfc-4QV3qr0wqF-h6A5FqLux7Vyw_baeTBdSnydq2KriNrfkAxaO-X737lKsD6NHE_YnD5k7owvFOo48GcPyDpPV5sGcHWtHbDkgMdqMVM1dDHpYH5pErMaT-4=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1rx1fmGXJ8h9Ra5GQ-OtQPhubXkKl_-qra1Wyo4SUN47QNsvtxhVynjaTWU3e_RB8B7dXaLplsrCbGsgvPo95spT9q3lxm4bBGCgI9zd-XME3JqCccVLT-IxNJxH6m6iihHa4hig=k-no"], "When": "2025-4-10"}, {"Name": "Donna Gutierrez", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3IT49ABm2bBncihtnmTsTjXe0WdNixPVdiOXhRcbcOKwTcCf8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Easily one of my favorite courts. Love the cafe beside it, the court surface, and the restroom is clean and spacious", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2CzSBCxKYNwbs9uWxDKeTbyfo4va8LyqvS35wnPZgjbTck1id6glNhgCvxGjLXfKmAMNBCxuz-0sCWbPmCTZkmx5yok744QBOmSq9aICUDRU_htQgWOlLqKlmrpdDq1nYk4qecOE9pMGZG=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3LgU7zo9VoLwkxstg4K8e5tz-Ds_iCu8-JXXkDL1TCEmvvFKTdS9o7R1-zw8dyKhUkil9XxmklHR1yzcSnqU1sNFnRZXHPwz29oakWwGzedG5O-ShoTPnnxQN0goHBIF9oO_We7ktWhVU=k-no"], "When": "2026-1-7"}, {"Name": "Svetlana", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoTW8_sNwkhGBXGv87ATUyVGvgcJe1asYXscksBf4Ru2YzNg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "I absolutely love this pickleball court! The location is perfect and easy to get to, and the entire facility is always clean and well-maintained. The restrooms are spotless, which is something I really appreciate. The staff are always kind, friendly, and ready to help with anything you need.\n\nThey also provide high-quality paddles and balls, so you don’t have to worry about bringing your own. The place itself is beautiful, the design and atmosphere make playing here a real pleasure. And to top it all off, they have their own bar with drinks, which is a great way to relax after a game. Highly recommend this place!", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Bonny Missy", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVB-jX8ChvYcguuWQryabknEqBMEIgX7lfQLkahOM0iZrMhHTCp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "The court is rather hot after 10am. The owners and people here are just too friendly and hilarious There’s also a lovely air-conditioned cafe which we could hang around after matches. Cheapest and most fun court I ever been to :)", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Матвей Кострыгин", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxQrd588Cq-KNUH5_vkfFljyVfj7boIA1R75cCblWVKhOT9A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Very good place. High-quality surface, cool enough even in the middle of the day, everything you need.\nThe only thing that gets in the way is people who enter the playing areas early, walk around, for some reason change there (although there is enough space for this) and this interferes with the game. And no one controls them. In all the other places I''ve been, people enter the court only after the previous players have left.\nOtherwise, a great place!", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "En Ka", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqL82vI8cIw_vS1ICbfwNEa5F4yc-WAiZuba5nxVZlyFx94w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100", "Rating": 1, "Description": "I am a neighbor living there a long time before you opened and hearing you every day from 5am until sometimes to 23:30pm. Yes, not just 22:30 but as late as 23:30pm. You need to protect the community around you from the sound of it.\nPeople yelling and the sound when a bat hits the pickleball is going through the air and into the neighborhood with no walls to protect us from you. Every day. From early to late. Do something about this and build proper soundproof.", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "CELINA BROOK", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzkOZTNq_z19MUNtNyfszySS7hFGWXSiLSmlpTh7AuQRlS8Rp9Lg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Excellent 2 court. Well kept. Clean. Covered or they even ask if you want it uncovered. They provide nice paddles and there are lots of balls. 120k drop in. After there is a perfect cafe right here to enjoy your cafe moui", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1bDpsOjOnrT65QNIBqQ11uuwUuJlqGZntO6TCNbAcnhLzxCaqyJpduWn5KAnyaDEiqKlToEgWYcYH5SZyGE6r_GfAyQuo7JgdXH5LZSK0kHB2FOZvBXdvTfgic3S0DvjDy_X0=k-no"], "When": "2025-3-26"}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday": {"10": 31, "11": 34, "12": 36, "13": 31, "14": 31, "15": 31, "16": 31, "17": 25, "18": 23, "19": 23, "20": 17, "21": 12, "22": 0, "4": 0, "5": 29, "6": 31, "7": 29, "8": 23, "9": 23}, "Monday": {"10": 21, "11": 23, "12": 29, "13": 36, "14": 34, "15": 31, "16": 38, "17": 44, "18": 48, "19": 57, "20": 55, "21": 48, "22": 0, "4": 0, "5": 25, "6": 23, "7": 23, "8": 19, "9": 23}, "Saturday": {"10": 36, "11": 36, "12": 36, "13": 38, "14": 40, "15": 38, "16": 36, "17": 25, "18": 27, "19": 27, "20": 40, "21": 38, "22": 0, "4": 0, "5": 27, "6": 38, "7": 53, "8": 61, "9": 44}, "Sunday": {"10": 51, "11": 46, "12": 36, "13": 36, "14": 36, "15": 31, "16": 34, "17": 38, "18": 40, "19": 38, "20": 34, "21": 23, "22": 0, "4": 0, "5": 19, "6": 31, "7": 46, "8": 53, "9": 61}, "Thursday": {"10": 42, "11": 48, "12": 59, "13": 55, "14": 48, "15": 36, "16": 34, "17": 29, "18": 27, "19": 40, "20": 36, "21": 34, "22": 0, "4": 0, "5": 17, "6": 17, "7": 19, "8": 25, "9": 38}, "Tuesday": {"10": 55, "11": 48, "12": 42, "13": 34, "14": 27, "15": 19, "16": 17, "17": 17, "18": 27, "19": 34, "20": 34, "21": 31, "22": 0, "4": 0, "5": 19, "6": 27, "7": 31, "8": 36, "9": 46}, "Wednesday": {"10": 19, "11": 23, "12": 25, "13": 31, "14": 27, "15": 34, "16": 40, "17": 57, "18": 74, "19": 100, "20": 97, "21": 76, "22": 0, "4": 0, "5": 29, "6": 29, "7": 25, "8": 19, "9": 17}}'::jsonb, '[{"id": "service_options", "name": "Service options", "options": [{"name": "Onsite services", "enabled": true}]}, {"id": "payments", "name": "Payments", "options": [{"name": "Credit cards", "enabled": true}]}]'::jsonb, ARRAY['Pickleball court', 'Credit cards', 'Onsite services'], NULL, '05:30', '22:30') ON CONFLICT (place_id) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, address = EXCLUDED.address, city = EXCLUDED.city, district = EXCLUDED.district, lat = EXCLUDED.lat, lng = EXCLUDED.lng, rating = EXCLUDED.rating, rating_count = EXCLUDED.rating_count, phone = EXCLUDED.phone, google_maps_url = EXCLUDED.google_maps_url, booking_url = EXCLUDED.booking_url, thumbnail_url = EXCLUDED.thumbnail_url, images = EXCLUDED.images, opening_hours = EXCLUDED.opening_hours, reviews_data = EXCLUDED.reviews_data, popular_times = EXCLUDED.popular_times, amenities = EXCLUDED.amenities, tags = EXCLUDED.tags, highlight = EXCLUDED.highlight, hours_open = EXCLUDED.hours_open, hours_close = EXCLUDED.hours_close;
INSERT INTO public.courts (name, address, city, district, lat, lng, rating, rating_count, phone, google_maps_url, booking_url, place_id, thumbnail_url, images, opening_hours, reviews_data, popular_times, amenities, tags, highlight, hours_open, hours_close) VALUES ('Ariyana Pickleball Centre - Cung hội nghị quốc tế Ariyana Đà Nẵng', '107 Vo Nguyen Giap Str., Ngu Hanh Son Ward, 107 Võ Nguyên Giáp, Khuê Mỹ, Ngũ Hành Sơn, Đà Nẵng 550000, Vietnam', 'Da Nang', 'Khuê Mỹ, Ngu Hanh Son', 16.037899, 108.252001, 5.0, 82, '+84 915 703 557', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Ariyana+Pickleball+Centre+-+Cung+h%E1%BB%99i+ngh%E1%BB%8B+qu%E1%BB%91c+t%E1%BA%BF+Ariyana+%C4%90%C3%A0+N%E1%BA%B5ng/data=!4m7!3m6!1s0x3142172150042035:0x23e0d1759081c64a!8m2!3d16.037899!4d108.2520008!16s%2Fg%2F11xctzvzmn!19sChIJNSAEUCEXQjERSsaBkHXR4CM?authuser=0&hl=en&rclk=1', 'https://ariyanacentre.com/ariyana-pickleball-centre/', 'ChIJNSAEUCEXQjERSsaBkHXR4CM', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHARtPtLsoJNDfB65CbY0w_ZwaSYkwiVtSe3CgEZP7ZAMAedutnTUCsxm9Gj9NLEfr_QFGtZ4TMllTWX21kElNuBlZjMDPR5Jj2CmlcjQ3suZQbyhD-rZfTI_ah9FtxFLoD4zWjDhaubVRY=w408-h271-k-no', '[{"title": "All", "image": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHARtPtLsoJNDfB65CbY0w_ZwaSYkwiVtSe3CgEZP7ZAMAedutnTUCsxm9Gj9NLEfr_QFGtZ4TMllTWX21kElNuBlZjMDPR5Jj2CmlcjQ3suZQbyhD-rZfTI_ah9FtxFLoD4zWjDhaubVRY=w447-h298-k-no"}, {"title": "Latest", "image": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEMuswyv3QhxgGIMV6kZ3ha_IdcpaF-vkjsfbm46pTgHHWtBJ6ONKk5G8YnRC9kP0d5i1vdVG98kXfKdva2oVVP4L7tBhyKFMbPaVOgos94rOuyCDYbduSO8-aujeRUa8sdXOmGIpd5FY_j=w224-h502-k-no"}, {"title": "Videos", "image": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGcNEOd6Qr7JjJZomjUipznpquBWBtpaRb8ZmoDd4NlocmZabDtRY6apiMfneM41ZGfmE49iskVTs0IiqdeobvGZUOeF65IY7yPyre-04cXmuPj3OvkTU-EQ7i4bqZzIvw45BGOkzT9DK8=w224-h398-k-no"}, {"title": "By owner", "image": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGcNEOd6Qr7JjJZomjUipznpquBWBtpaRb8ZmoDd4NlocmZabDtRY6apiMfneM41ZGfmE49iskVTs0IiqdeobvGZUOeF65IY7yPyre-04cXmuPj3OvkTU-EQ7i4bqZzIvw45BGOkzT9DK8=w224-h398-k-no"}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday": ["5:30 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Monday": ["5:30 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Saturday": ["5:30 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Sunday": ["5:30 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Thursday": ["5:30 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Tuesday": ["5:30 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Wednesday": ["5:30 a.m.–10 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name": "Matthew Smith", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlppmDw9H1gG_qe2Cf-MV-MD0u7CiVNwU50wIB-EaT3tBXp-wv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Just playing some amazing Pickleball at the centre. Fantastic high-quality courts. I also booked a Pickleball lesson with the pro Son, Who took me through drills and was very helpful. Look forward to playing again and highly recommend.", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2f2dcTAAWZHjJ6rkYS4JJ5wxQi8AWbqRXsgKKur7XzrJhEnU2Yw29a6Q3qUWlAm3pi4qS8USDkj-oL1hh3LODMySS2adssBEj9Crvc8MZfo1UrE3c74TdJ-A8KngSlgkwCDb_q7UyQ7sk=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3QTZMw_znIyDczCAwKcFb_s6vCIA9ppTbK-_vs8KR_rD9-NYv1LpUZoGP82JRm_atnNhjwUw1ZnmUkw5mK8f-9gPU9r0gkExS-8JOvZyaNfnw9Ct7cn6wfwQ-DQO1_QVTb9TQER9d_3DHJ=k-no"], "When": "2026-1-6"}, {"Name": "Sora Kim", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaW0F8UHqDjb1QChUNFBwkl-YmGQscz4MHXWXE-bEljcjYvpzp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️\nTitle: Excellent Service from Kim Thanh at Furama Resort\n\nI had a wonderful experience at Furama Resort. During my time playing pickleball here, Ms. Kim Thanh was extremely kind, enthusiastic, and helpful. She made sure everything went smoothly and always greeted guests with a warm smile. Her positive energy made my visit even more enjoyable.\n\nThank you, Kim Thanh, for your great service and cheerful attitude — you truly represent the spirit of Furama Resort! I’ll definitely come back again.", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Dennis Schmelz", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7XA8guls78CbAy8PA4MB0MYIr7K6_-dnkpcH1E22C0ViXdQgf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "First pickleball experience with our private trainer Són, it was a lot of fun. A mix of tennis and badminton, really enjoyed this one hour with my wife.", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "kim kneipp", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIm9npgxekhI7sATFBvMfxcCpDH0fITyjto3KFA09KvcGQONw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Mr Hai was so attentive and helpful and even joined in to play pickleball with me and my sons. He’s a great player! Fun for all the family", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Chloe Georgia", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJXQDvKUEb-JtO1sA36puJTsQ0d6Byn47ppaoGJw73l_9mQzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Such a good activity during your travels, so much fun", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Hoang Tran", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUajZWMQvxiNbAu_XDlCwtCztFbwhnFKP7gkUygp0oss6WW2Isd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Nice courts and staffs.", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2_0I8gIndhJU6iNxGImfE8WYKFnkH7x5q6cJ8vU1TMpPBc3lnwrjnMuRVCIE-91kv1NoVrwWTYsxIS5DkerjfAuBMT5MnpkmnrnIx1dbyvg-d2JYhjWdeZQjyQPMvy2phZtZiMIho3yfM=k-no"], "When": "2026-1-10"}, {"Name": "Raymond Dissinger", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuIRKiofBD4LKE0UQm2Nec0E4INedDw5UjWtJij6n94hmEwKfk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "So much fuch my first time and very easy.", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Phuong Le", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4Lb2QTEmvTny5KfurStXUqXVuY44nT7mw_fL4uhNz4mau4sQJ-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Great courts. Ms. Thanh is very friendly and helpful.", "Images": null, "When": ""}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday": {"10": 22, "11": 16, "12": 11, "13