, "Description": "Great courts with covering from rain or sun. 4 courts and paddles/balls to use if needed. The self-service made it super easy and convenient. Definitely would come back :-)", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2dJIk2mTbEBHrtOaRDGRNep8YU54Bq_kEm5ChIaDw5A2wfuUyZ7PntDCJWeUXVNHNju411PkbTU18oy99i2n1IezhNdtyl5oonuaKd3u67lmWnZhLbf1zEtNVosNCDWLDf__IrXL-sJVE=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3xCpOW8yJp4F77cXE1uaPrxq-mYYGvOXKxlq2PIdoZNrH6Zd-IqpKg-k0c07lMInm72ryKwlO_aw0w61-dTcQw8Vosm-J2-2odlyETKakNw4GEaS4GHFinhD83fMS2KoBSq4rC_gRmWINh=k-no"], "When": "2025-8-12"}, {"Name": "Wanwan Gao", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWn8eepHb99HjUsoT1lkPGoOJEsR8QTQ_1OJ-UWtbRCVXCQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "First time we visited here was a wonderful experience! Both me and my daughter enjoyed a lot with the activities especially the Pickleball, we had lots of fun!\n\nIt is a large outdoor area, but it is protected from the sun and can accommodate dozens of people at the same time. There are many ball games, which are especially suitable for people who want to exercise. Adults, children, the elderly, men, women and all age can play. We had a lot of fun there yesterday, and there are drinks and some snacks to replenish energy during the break. We will come back again, If I have more stars, I will definitely give more stars to this place. It is perfect for taking children to exercise together and if you would like to see handsome man and beautiful lady here, good choice as well for this reason🤣", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Justin Sachon", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUm31zhARTV2GOTW0vXENX5Ui3r4K-RWIK5Kc767JhpCvDnE9U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Self-service pickleball courts with nice managers. Provides balls and paddles. Great business.", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Sebastian Buck", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJlnJNPNZ2_YMdAER63RZwk2wW2aPSBRqKNJnD_CvYYkFukww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Best pickle ball court in town!", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0w3-AcckWrprx0uyS9mPcyLOjFM6wSGRiw_g59iIZqdeJyX8ZrdUyIEEh7aTInnoOrcaVP8MV-cNVEOSXkIHf1xOiCM9N9V_MUIIEEdmbI-2iCFus3RcBfNVO-I2SzfaPx9ObrtxKsZ_o0=k-no"], "When": "2025-12-1"}, {"Name": "huyền hồ thanh", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTkD6zRec1G7M0nGqqLDZGeLSIiwdFZ245ZZZwaEdv_8jaHfay=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Sân đẹp, dịch vụ tốt.\nĐiểm hẹn lý tưởng dịp cuối tuần cho mọi người ❤️", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Юлия Гусева", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5KrDEG-CJY7CUVV7kcvCrsmKVu-UEplWUOfUKLABRyNG5QWyJIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Давно хотели поиграть в пиклбол и тут рядом с нами открылся этот корт. Всё сошлось 🙂 здесь всё новое, 4 корта, хорошие ракетки и мячи.\nТеперь будем часто приходить.\nЛучи поддержки ребятам🖤", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn25nEcvMTZzljmuGGn724AqcMDSwRf0jzaqBmySDk-1NpKzgiELOsj-NnDzLuQctkjpVsbWPH4kbpKRtFhWJxuPwY8n3VvTQM_gayWEcStrg6B6Ri65pHXf1nOoQHpkd_SbOcSNNw=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1WsNKgjoDCddNWmEC8KRISkol7UHcMSdQs-O7bEwtupmD56v-KM4OlJHw7tC0CBDmgkQvAU5Qj4GJShpZrqR3tcs_WHFIQfxAB5LmDnl1wLZHWa9887LUn0vJEl3v0W9E8YR8KIg=k-no"], "When": "2025-4-12"}, {"Name": "Minh Nguyễn", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfv64tcCxAVcrhqe6WA_ZAZA90pe3d7y7ha2eUcA0RrJPU2w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 1, "Description": "Sân quá bẩn bùn quá nhiều ko vệ sinh sân", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Cam Diep", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrtJNaybmlitxhcm1FQJwK9GiZ8IAqNIuBXXrbexpAv2qrcF0n=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Tuyệt vời quá. Cảm ơn anh chủ đã ưu ái cho các bé đến sử dụng miễn phí", "Images": null, "When": ""}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday": {"10": 67, "11": 50, "12": 39, "13": 35, "14": 46, "15": 50, "16": 57, "17": 67, "18": 71, "19": 57, "20": 50, "21": 39, "22": 0, "5": 0, "6": 21, "7": 39, "8": 53, "9": 75}, "Monday": {"10": 21, "11": 25, "12": 32, "13": 53, "14": 71, "15": 75, "16": 60, "17": 60, "18": 57, "19": 60, "20": 60, "21": 60, "22": 0, "5": 0, "6": 14, "7": 17, "8": 25, "9": 21}, "Saturday": {"10": 42, "11": 50, "12": 35, "13": 42, "14": 57, "15": 82, "16": 100, "17": 100, "18": 89, "19": 60, "20": 46, "21": 32, "22": 0, "5": 0, "6": 28, "7": 39, "8": 32, "9": 42}, "Sunday": {"10": 28, "11": 25, "12": 17, "13": 14, "14": 21, "15": 35, "16": 57, "17": 60, "18": 64, "19": 46, "20": 35, "21": 17, "22": 0, "5": 0, "6": 35, "7": 50, "8": 50, "9": 46}, "Thursday": {"10": 46, "11": 50, "12": 46, "13": 42, "14": 35, "15": 42, "16": 67, "17": 89, "18": 89, "19": 82, "20": 50, "21": 42, "22": 0, "5": 0, "6": 28, "7": 17, "8": 21, "9": 35}, "Tuesday": {"10": 42, "11": 46, "12": 35, "13": 35, "14": 35, "15": 50, "16": 67, "17": 82, "18": 89, "19": 64, "20": 46, "21": 32, "22": 0, "5": 0, "6": 14, "7": 28, "8": 35, "9": 46}, "Wednesday": {"10": 17, "11": 17, "12": 28, "13": 21, "14": 25, "15": 28, "16": 46, "17": 60, "18": 64, "19": 57, "20": 32, "21": 28, "22": 0, "5": 0, "6": 46, "7": 42, "8": 42, "9": 25}}'::jsonb, NULL, ARRAY['Pickleball court'], NULL, '06:00', '22:00') ON CONFLICT (place_id) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, address = EXCLUDED.address, city = EXCLUDED.city, district = EXCLUDED.district, lat = EXCLUDED.lat, lng = EXCLUDED.lng, rating = EXCLUDED.rating, rating_count = EXCLUDED.rating_count, phone = EXCLUDED.phone, google_maps_url = EXCLUDED.google_maps_url, booking_url = EXCLUDED.booking_url, thumbnail_url = EXCLUDED.thumbnail_url, images = EXCLUDED.images, opening_hours = EXCLUDED.opening_hours, reviews_data = EXCLUDED.reviews_data, popular_times = EXCLUDED.popular_times, amenities = EXCLUDE